**What will be the output of the following Java program?**
```java
class Demo {
    Demo() {
        System.out.println("Constructor Called");
    }

    void show() {
        System.out.println("Hello, Java!");
    }
}

 class Seedit {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Demo obj = new Demo();
        obj.show();
    }
}
```

